Installation and configuration for Ubuntu 18.04 LTS

Download the latest .deb file from http://wps-community.org/downloads

Install the .deb file.

sudo dpkg -i wps*

Create the .font folder in Terminal

sudo mkdir ~/.fonts

cd /tmp

git clone https://github.com/iamdh4/ttf-wps-fonts.git

cd /tmp/ttf-wps-fonts

cd ~/.fonts

sudo cp /tmp/ttf-wps-fonts/* . && sudo rm -rf /tmp/ttf*


Re-launch Writer
